Payment Vnpay Refund Activity: execute the validated workflow

start
:Payment Vnpay Refund Activity: execute the validated workflow;
:Build refundRequest (vnp_RequestId, vnp_TxnRef, ...);
:Payment Vnpay Refund Activity: execute the validated workflow;
if (condition?) then (Yes)
